actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Interior and Insular Affairs.

official_title: A bill to authorize and direct the Secretary of the Interior to sell interests of the United States in certain lands located in the State of Alaska to the Gospel Missionary Union.

summary.text: Authorizes and directs the Secretary of the Interior to sell interests of the United States in certain lands located in the state of Alaska to the Gospel Missionary Union.
